ent toward science and computer resources tuition assistance and the athletic department in  and in honor of farleys contributions to the school the west annex building at st raphael was renamed barbara farley hall in honor of farleys mother farley has made numerous contributions over the years to the american heart association and hes been a donor to and board member of various civic and cultural organizations in his adopted hometown of chicago illinois including the goodman theater the lyric opera house and the chicago council on foreign relations he has also sat on the board of directors for the horatio alger association awards and honorsedit  farley is recognized as outstanding business graduate of the year by the boston college law school alumni association  farley receives the horatio alger association of distinguished americans award the award is given to community leaders who demonstrate individual initiative and a commitment to excellence as exemplified by remarkable achievements accomplished through honesty hard work selfreliance and perseverance over adversity  farley is inducted into the rhode island heritage hall of fame and is honored by the boys  girls club of america as a businesscommunity honoree of the year  honored by the irelandus council for commerce and industry for outstanding achievement for his work in economics business and commercial activity he also is named one of irishamerica magazines top  businessmen and receives the white houses presidential award for entrepreneurial excellence  farley is honored with a freedom award from americas freedom festival at provo personal lifeedit farley was a high school athlete at st raphael academy in pawtucket rhode island and played three varsity sports football swimming and baseball at bowdoin he provided financial support to the athletic departments at st raphael and bowdoin in the s farley became a minority owner of the chicago white sox farley was an active member in the young presidents organization he is currently a member of the world presidents organization he has also been a member of the chicago club and the university associates of northwestern university for years farley lives in chicago with his wife shelley a cabaret singer who has performed michael feinstein george burns and president bill clinton farley has three sons the youngest liam lives in chicago with him his two older sons hayes macarthur and scott live in los angeles referencesedit  a b c d labich kenneth may   bill farley has a dream machine fortune  a b c d e f g chiappinelli bob july   pawtuckets horatio alger providence sunday journal  a b klein amy may   schools benefactor renames building for his mother the providence journalbulletin  a b c d sheridan mike april  profile william f farley echelon magazine  a b c bill farley casts a wide net for companies financial enterprise summer   herguth bob january   chicago profile william f farley chicago suntimes  sheridan mike april  profile william f farley echelon magazine  a b c cs january   the buyout man us news  world report  farleynorthwest to sell subsidiary tribunedigitalchicagotribune retrieved    northwest industries wwwnndbcom retrieved    a major deal maker of the s is drowning in debt in the s los angeles times retrieved   check date values in accessdate help  west point pepperell buyer steps down as its chairman new york times retrieved    fruit of loom back as farley makes changes tribunedigitalchicagotribune retrieved    bill farley the handson conglomerator industry week june    a b c d e delaney patricia  farley chair in legal studies endowed boston college chronicle   harvey tom february   utah drink firm in meltdown the salt lake tribune  harvey tom february   utah drink firm in meltdown the salt lake tribune  a major deal maker of the s is drowning in debt in the s los angeles times retrieved   check date values in accessdate help  harvey tom may   draper company launches zrii says its a healthful juice the salt lake tri