ed most analysts agree with mr farley that his pruning of northwest in particular has been worthwhile among the moves he has made are taking a  million loss on the sale of the pogo producing company an oil and gas exploration company and selling for  million the agrichemical division of the troubled velsicol chemical corporation he plans to sell the small remaining portion of velsicol by the end of the year what remains in the northwest unit are one stellar business  union underwear which markets under the fruit of the loom and bvd labels  and two solid but less impressive operations  the general battery corporation the nations secondlargest maker of replacement batteries for cars and acme boot whose products include the dingo footwear line a slimmer northwest beefed up by increased spending for such things as advertising has considerable profit potential according to leon d black a managing director at drexel burnham lambert inc the picture had been cloudy because of velsicol he said but with the asset sales the numbers have already improved in a short period what remains at northwest he said is a future that looks very good two leading brands with fruit of the loom and bvd union controls  percent of the massmerchandise underwear market the unit had  sales of  million and operating income of about  million generating about  percent of the northwest units operating income analysts say union has a strong history fruit of the loom did to mens underwear what hanes did to ladies nylons said w dudley herr an analyst with duff  phelps they marketed underwear away from department stores to just about any retail outlet  grocery stores five and dimes you name it and it is here that mr farley has his biggest plans hoping to capitalize on its distribution base farley will begin to strongly promote womens underwear as well as add mens and womens socks and sweatshirts to unions product line later this year according to mr farleys estimates socks and sweatshirts will add about  million in sales in  increasing unions product line will not be easy cautioned w dudley herr an analyst at duff  phelps stores just dont give a lot of play to fruit of the loom products now he said how hes going to get places like k mart to clear even more shelf space is anybodys guess if union is the strongest part of the farley empire analysts say condec is the weak spot in  he bought the  percent of condec that he did not own for  million for the year ending in july  the latest figures available condec had a loss of  million on revenues of  million in  it lost  million mr farley said condec was not very healthy when he purchased it  an assertion that is disputed by some former condec officials a pentagon investigation the condec troubles have not been limited to finances condiesel a unit has been the target of a  million department of defense overcharge investigation to make matters worse its largest contract carriage assemblies for howitzer armored vehicles expired this month   next page    inside nytimescom health raquo too hot to handle arts » the harmony of liberty opinion » should beach privatization be allowed room for debate asks whether shorefront homeowners should have to open their land to all comers sports » a woman’s leadership may steady murray opinion » menagerie streaming eagles us » curlers’ aim sweep to a win over the heat television » the cold war brews anew in prime time book review » command performance opinion » oped fooling mexican fans world » reading writing and allegations opinion » oped elite separate unequal new york city’s top public schools must become more diverse business » vice has media giants salivating bill farley  zrii  william f farley  zrii founder home personal education health prosperity giving my dream company farley william f inmate  boone county jail in florence ky bailbond blog contact us privacy policy toggle navigation bail bond city home inmate directory search alabama inmate directory search arizona inmate directory 